    <h4 class="myheadings">RX-V375</h4>
    <div class="thecontent"> <br>
      <p><img src="images/RX-V375.jpg"></p>
      <p><img src="images/RX-V375_tech.jpg"></p>
      <h3>Key Features:</h3>
      <p>• Discrete amplifier configuration</p>
      <p>• 100W x 5 (6O, 1 kHz, 0.9% THD)</p>
      <p>• 4 in/1 out HDMI with 3D, ARC and CEC</p>
      <p>• Front USB port<br>
        - Direct digital connection for iPod/iPhone<br>
        - iPod/iPhone charging in standby mode<br>
        - AAC, MP3, WMA and WAV decoding (up to 48 kHz)</p>
      <p>• Mass storage device support (MSC)</p>
