    <div class="thecontent"> <br>
      <p><img src="images/RX-V2073.jpg" width="100%"></p>
      <p><img src="images/RX-V2073_tech.jpg"></p>
      <h3>Upsell Features over RX-V1075:</h3>
      <p>• 140W x 9 (8O, 20 Hz - 20 kHz, 0.06% THD)</p>
      <p>• 9 channel amplifier</p>
      <p>• Subwoofer mode<br>
        - Stereo<br>
        - Front/Rear</p>
      <p>• CINEMA DSP 3D with Rear Presence</p>
