        - Zone 3 audio<br>
        - Zone 2 GUI</p>
      <p>• Compressed Music Enhancer</p>
      <p>• High Resolution mode</p>
      <p>• Automatic video adjustment</p>
      <p>• Analogue to Analogue video conversion</p>
      <p>• 40-200Hz Crossover frequency setting for each speaker</p>
      <p>• LCD Macro remote</p>
